high_descs: Head to the counter on the right side of the sink.
Open the cabinet above the counter and take out a plate and close it.
Move to your left to the sink beside you.
Place the plate in the sink and turn the water faucet on and rinse the plate off, after you turn the faucet off pick the plate back up.
Turn to your right and head to the table beside the refrigerator.
Place the plate down on the table in front of the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Clean a plate and put on the dining table.

high_descs: Move a step forward to the counter.
Open the cabinet above, and take out a plate. Shut the doors.
Hold the plate and take a step to the left, to find the sink.
Place the plate in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the plate.
Carry the plate and turn to the right, then right again. Move forward to the round table. Turn left, and face it on the right.
Place the plate on the left front side of the table.
anns.task_desc: Clean a plate and place it on the table.

high_descs: Walk over to the counter and look up at the upper cabinets.
Open the upper cabinet in front of you and take out the dirty grey plate, then close the cabinet.
Turn left and walk over to the sink.
Put the dirty grey plate in the sink and turn on the water,, after a couple seconds turn the water off and take out the now clean grey plate.
Walk over to the round wooden table in the corner of the room behind you.
Put the clean grey plate on the wooden table in between the bottles of lotion.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean grey plate on a table.
